  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《蓝实战队》</h2>是一款融合了大逃杀、撤离、市场交易生存类竞技游戏，在最多可容纳60人的竞技场里，跳伞，奔跑，收集，偷袭，瞄准，狙击，生存的地方会越来越小，紧张刺激，活到最后或撤离成功获得胜利。战局中获得的战利品，可以留下来自己用，或市场上进行售卖。获得的现金，可以用来购买更好的装备，带到之后的战局中。<br><br>抢先体验已结束，服务器停止运营<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >丛林作战跳伞，选择有利地势，决定战局</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1448400/extras/fc26e1d9720f31ff8491ffd2aa4d0d0f.avif?t=1723040067\" width=616 height=140 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >瞄准偷袭，先发制人</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1448400/extras/21d86dfe81882a0cb73e8a6b3e1a996a.avif?t=1723040067\" width=616 height=140 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >玩家需要到达地图中指定的撤离点，想尽办法活下来</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1448400/extras/b8eb3b3cc9a1079de8df0d95d28b8398.avif?t=1723040067\" width=616 height=140 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >玩家生存的地方会越来越小</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1448400/extras/1edb169ca4f5c1a5063a5851bc447378.avif?t=1723040067\" width=616 height=301 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >获得的战利品在市场交易，获得金币</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1448400/extras/5df246599c35f413cfa63c4e8b91307c.avif?t=1723040067\" width=616 height=347 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >训练场，勤加训练，赢战场凯旋</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1448400/extras/a1b7281af02cf15f407bf78609af931b.avif?t=1723040067\" width=616 height=347 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1448400/extras/0f44b8e17d9a5852e3e7322a5da71ed7.avif?t=1723040067\" width=616 height=256 /></span><br><br>开局保持耐心，推荐从军事基地后门进收集武器，打进车库上层，成功撤离，不然会太难，祝大家好运！<br><a href=\"mailto:问题联系：dlysk99@126.com\">问题联系：dlysk99@126.com</a>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《蓝实战队》</h2>是一款融合了大逃杀、撤离、市场交易生存类竞技游戏，在最多可容纳60人的竞技场里，跳伞，奔跑，收集，偷袭，瞄准，狙击，生存的地方会越来越小，紧张刺激，活到最后或撤离成功获得胜利。战局中获得的战利品，可以留下来自己用，或市场上进行售卖。获得的现金，可以用来购买更好的装备，带到之后的战局中。<br><br>抢先体验已结束，服务器停止运营<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >丛林作战跳伞，选择有利地势，决定战局</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1448400/extras/fc26e1d9720f31ff8491ffd2aa4d0d0f.avif?t=1723040067\" width=616 height=140 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >瞄准偷袭，先发制人</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1448400/extras/21d86dfe81882a0cb73e8a6b3e1a996a.avif?t=1723040067\" width=616 height=140 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >玩家需要到达地图中指定的撤离点，想尽办法活下来</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1448400/extras/b8eb3b3cc9a1079de8df0d95d28b8398.avif?t=1723040067\" width=616 height=140 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >玩家生存的地方会越来越小</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1448400/extras/1edb169ca4f5c1a5063a5851bc447378.avif?t=1723040067\" width=616 height=301 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >获得的战利品在市场交易，获得金币</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1448400/extras/5df246599c35f413cfa63c4e8b91307c.avif?t=1723040067\" width=616 height=347 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >训练场，勤加训练，赢战场凯旋</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1448400/extras/a1b7281af02cf15f407bf78609af931b.avif?t=1723040067\" width=616 height=347 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1448400/extras/0f44b8e17d9a5852e3e7322a5da71ed7.avif?t=1723040067\" width=616 he